; Hub — Wave 2 atmospheric upgrade. Adds:
; - ParallaxBackground with two layers: a deep cosmic nebula far layer
;   (scroll 0.05) and a silhouette skyline mid layer (scroll 0.2). Both
;   tile via motion_mirroring so the camera can roam the full Hub width
;   without seams.
; - A semi-transparent fog band across the horizon line, softening the
;   sky-floor seam so the floor doesn't read as cut-out.
; - A slow-rotating void Sprite2D inside each door's arch interior. One
;   shared AnimationPlayer animation drives all three voids at one
;   rotation per 60s (relative track path "Visual/Void:rotation").
; Wave 1 skeleton (procedural sky gradient, three placeholder doors,
; firefly particles) remains; the gradient sky is removed in favor of
; the parallax nebula since the nebula carries its own vertical fade.
